    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cafe-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "（あれ、こころちゃん……？　今日はオフって）\n（言ってたけど、一人で何してるんだろ……？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Huh‚ Kokoro-chan…? She said today was her day off‚）\n（what's she doing alone…?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.7333335161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.1000001828
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "ふむふむ……この時のパフォーマンスは\nこんな感じで加点されてるんだ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm-hmm… this is how the points\nwere added to the performance…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.1000001828,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "てことは、もう少し全体的に振り付けを大きくして\nみたら……あ、でもそうするとここの数値が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ if we make the choreography a little more bigger\noverall… Ah‚ but then the numbers here are…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.1000001907,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.9000012636
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～VENUSプログラムの解析にはクセがあるって\nmihoさんが言ってたから少し調べてみてるけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa~‚ miho-san said there are rules for interpreting the VENUS program‚\nso I looked into it a bit",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.9000012636,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり難しいな～。数字を見るのは嫌いじゃないから\n慣れれば出来そうかもだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it's really difficult~. I don't mind reading numbers‚\nso I think I could do it once I got used to it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.3000068586,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.3333379031
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "やっほー、こころちゃん！　何してるの～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yahooー‚ Kokoro-chan! What are you doing~?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.3333379031,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.2666753055
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "うわぁっ！？　すすすみれちゃん！？　別にこころは\n何もしてません！　そろそろ帰るところです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoa!? S-S-Sumire-chan!? Kokoro didn't\nreally do anything! Just about to go back!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.2666753055,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6999.99365
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.2000086388
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "お片付け、お片付け～っと\n帰る準備～、帰る準備～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Cleaning‚ cleaning~ up\nReady to go back~‚ go back~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.2000086388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.9666753055
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "計算機が置いてある……ってことは\nもしかして学校の宿題してたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's a calculator… so‚\ndid you do your homework?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.9666753055,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.4666732711
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "まあ、そんな感じです～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ something like that~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.4666732711,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.3333399377
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "宿題は計算機使っちゃダメだよ！\n自分でやらないと身に付かないんだから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're not supposed to use a calculator for homework!\nIf you don't do it yourself‚ your body won't learn it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.3333399377,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.5333353601
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "分かってます、大丈夫です～！\n学校の課題じゃないですし、自習みたいなものなので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know‚ it's okay~!\nIt's not schoolwork‚ it's just self-study",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.7000024795,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.8000020268
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったんだ。勘違いしちゃってごめんね！\nこころちゃんて実は……やっぱりなんでもない！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. Sorry for misunderstanding!\nKokoro-chan is actually… Never mind!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.8000020268,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.3954616433
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.6666686935
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "なんですか～？\n途中まで言われると気になりますよ～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What is it~?\nI'm worried about when you stop while talking~?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.6666686935,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.6666666589
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "オフの日も勉強してるなんて偉いな～って\nお友達とワイワイ遊ぶ感じかなって思ってたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought it was great that you studied on your days off‚\nand that you would just hang out with your friends",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.6666666589,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.3333333256
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "なっ！　こころだって友達くらいいますし\n今日はたまたま一人でのんびりしてただけですよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What! Kokoro has some friends too!\nI was just relaxing alone today!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.3333333256,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.8666661504
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "本当にたまたまなんですからね？　まったく……\nすみれちゃんは酷いです～。こころ傷つきましたよ～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really just a coincidence? Seriously…\nSumire-chan is mean~. Kokoro was hurt~?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.8666661504,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.4333328171
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "ご、ごめんね……\nそんなつもりで言った訳じゃなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-Sorry…\nI didn't mean to…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.4333328171,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.6333292567
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "……というのは嘘で、一人で過ごすことが多いですよ\nたまにリズノワで遊びに行ったりしますけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That's a lie‚ I spend a lot of time alone\nSometimes I go to LizNoir to hang out",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.6333292567,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.8999959234
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "私も一緒！　お休みの日はトリエルで遊ぶか\n実家でのんびりしてることが多いかな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Me too! On my days off‚ I usually play with TRINITYAiLE\nor relax at my house~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.5333358128,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 139.1999959234
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "あ、そうだ！　もしこの後暇だったら一緒にお買い物\nしない？　文房具買いに行きたいんだ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ that's right! If you're free after this‚ would you like to go shopping\nwith me? I want to buy some stationery~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.1999959234,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147.1999959234
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_03-kkr013.m4a",
